```python id=bloq
import numpy as np
from qualtran.bloqs.basic_gates import YPowGate
# Ry(α) primitive, α=arccos(sqrt(1/6)) — W-state cascade 반각(k=6). 전역위상은 C4 무시.
bloq = YPowGate(exponent=np.arccos(np.sqrt(1/6))/np.pi)
```
```python id=golden
import numpy as np
a = np.arccos(np.sqrt(1/6))
golden = np.array([[np.cos(a/2), -np.sin(a/2)], [np.sin(a/2), np.cos(a/2)]], dtype=complex)
```
